text: The Heritage at Millennium Park is a skyscraper in Chicago, Illinois. It is located at 130 N. Garland Court. It is a mixed-use tower. Completed in 2005, with a height of 631 feet and 57 floors. ==Other websites== *The Heritage at Millennium Park Condominium Sales & Rental Website *Condominium Association website Category:Skyscrapers in Chicago Category:2005 establishments in Illinois
